Dependency libraries:

 - cjk-tokenizer: Routines for tokenising CJK text.  Copied from
   http://code.google.com/p/cjk-tokenizer/
 - jsoncpp 0.5.0: downloaded from
   http://downloads.sourceforge.net/project/jsoncpp/jsoncpp/0.5.0/jsoncpp-src-0.5.0.tar.gz?r=http%3A%2F%2Fsourceforge.net%2Fprojects%2Fjsoncpp%2F&ts=1283175966&use_mirror=sunet
 - libmicrohttpd: Downloaded from http://www.gnu.org/s/libmicrohttpd/.
 - lua: A lua interpreter: currently unused.
 - mongo-c-driver: Downloaded from
   https://github.com/mongodb/mongo-c-driver
 - unittest-cpp: Downloaded from
   https://unittest-cpp.svn.sourceforge.net/svnroot/unittest-cpp
 - xapiancommon: Some routines ripped from Xapian, that aren't exposed in
   Xapian's API.
